  "title": "Blockchain Development and Future Scope",
  "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-glow));\n      padding: 2rem;\n    }\n    .hero-container {\n      position: relative;\n      z-index: 10;\n      max-width: 900px;\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n    .hero-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);\n      line-height: 1.1;\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      background: var(--accent-gradient);\n      -webkit-background-clip: text;\n      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n      font-weight: 800;\n    }\n    .hero-subtitle {\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      max-width: 700px;\n      margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    .hero-pill {\n      display: inline-block;\n      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 50px;\n      font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 2px;\n      margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .decorative-ring {\n      position: absolute;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      opacity: 0.3;\n      pointer-events: none;\n      animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;\n    }\n    @keyframes rotate {\n      from { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes fadeInUp {\n      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <!-- Decorative Elements -->\n  <div class=\"decorative-ring\" style=\"width: 80vh; height: 80vh; top: calc(50% - 40vh); left: calc(50% - 40vh);\"></div>\n  <div class=\"decorative-ring\" style=\"width: 60vh; height: 60vh; top: calc(50% - 30vh); left: calc(50% - 30vh); animation-direction: reverse;\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"hero-container\">\n    <div class=\"reveal hero-pill visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.2s\">\n      Engineering the Decentralized Web\n    </div>\n    \n    <h1 class=\"reveal hero-title visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">\n      Blockchain Development and Future Scope\n    </h1>\n    \n    <p class=\"reveal hero-subtitle visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n      Exploring the evolution of decentralized ledger technology to bridge the gap between code and commerce. \n      A strategic roadmap for the next generation of developers and investors.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</section>",
